{"tid":1518463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日有基督教集合及遊行 如果大家係基督徒嘅一齊黎","createTime":"2019-08-30T09:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:21:44.000Z","uid":56537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd2b19e6190fb9c9315e358ddeddc755eafb43e","tid":1518463,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"【召集十萬基督徒為香港罪人祈禱大遊行】<br />\n<br />\n日期：31/8<br />\n時間：下午1230集合、1300起步<br />\n集合地點：灣仔修頓球場<br />\n遊行路線：軒尼詩道&rarr;金鐘道&rarr;花園道&rarr;上亞厘畢道<br />\n活動詳情：遊行至循道衛理、警察總部、聖約翰座堂對開的花園道及禮賓府時，將稍作停留進行讀經和唱聖詩。<br />\n註：由於是次活動為宗教活動，按公安條例可豁免向警方申請，是故將不會辦理不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n未信主嘅朋友當然可以一齊來祈禱！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#無俱白色恐怖 #港島見"},{"pid":"eb2c715d14861ec9c17b23e7d393fc38af509689","tid":1518463,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"兩句講哂<br />\n831無大台 出中環<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=8b880327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1u